(116, 4, 'en', 'actions-old', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 'Actions old', '', '', '<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>DEAR GUESTS!</b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b>We are happy to see you in our hotel and make a special proposal to you!</b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;</b><b>Happy</b><b>birthday</b><b>,&nbsp;</b><b>dear</b><b>guest</b><b>!&nbsp;</b>We would like to extend our felicitations on this wonderful day and to do something pleasant to you. There is saying: &laquo;My age is my treasure&raquo;. Therefore, we offer you 10% discount on this day.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</b><b>Discount</b><b>for</b><b>feedback</b><b>.</b>&nbsp;Give us your feedback on our hotel at our web-site:&nbsp;<b>hotel-uyut.kz</b>.Give us your contact information and we will give you 10% discount upon your next stay in our hotel.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>3. Call back.&nbsp;</b>Call back order. If you cannot call us right now because of any reasons, then you can order a back call and we will call you back without fail at the time most convenient to you. For this purpose, you need to send the following information to our E-mail<b>:&nbsp;</b><a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.ru\"><b>hotel_uyut@mail.ru</b></a><b>,&nbsp;</b><a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.kz\"><b>hotel_uyut@mail.kz</b></a><b>,</b><a href=\"mailto:reservation@hotel-uyut.kz\"><b>reservation@hotel-uyut.kz</b></a></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Your phone number;</li>\r\n    <li>Time that is best for the back call;</li>\r\n    <li>The way you would like us to address you.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>4.&nbsp;</b><b>Weekend</b><b>tariff</b><b>*.</b>&nbsp;If you would like to distract yourself from intense workdays and get charged with bright emotions, &ldquo;Uyut&rdquo; Hotel invites you to spend your weekend with us:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>2 nights stay: Friday through Sunday &ndash; 30% discount;</li>\r\n    <li>1 night stay: Friday through Sunday &ndash; 20% discount.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b><i>&nbsp;</i></b></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b><i>*This offer is valid subject to availability of vacant rooms. It does not apply to &ldquo;Economy&rdquo; category rooms.</i></b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>1. Offers for families who adopts the children from Kazakhstan</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The families with children can be provided with the following: extra bed if required; bassinets or playpen; potty; highchair; toys; device for heating of feeding bottles; electric kettle; two kinds of cooked cereals for breakfast, home-made milk and kefir, diabetic diet .</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>2. Packages for newly-married couples:</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Luxury two-room Lux-Suite decorated in wedding style;</li>\r\n    <li>shampagne bottle and fruits at the hotel&rsquo;s expense;</li>\r\n    <li>breakfast to the suite;</li>\r\n    <li>late check-out</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><b><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;</font></b></div>\r\n<h3>Permanent Guest Program:</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our hotel provides for the Permanent Guest Program. We offer the bonuses and discounts system which corresponds to the number of your guestrooms:</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><u>UYUT SILVER&nbsp;</u></strong>&ndash; after paying for 10 nights for the calendar year and filling the questionnaire you will be provided with UYUT SILVER card, and you will have a right to have the following bonuses and privileges: Guaranteed reservation (if the request is received not later than 72 hours before); Late check-out (16 hours); 5% discount for accommodation in Uyut hotel; 5% discount for Uyut restaurant services and mini-bar in the guestroom; Welcome Gift &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><u><strong>UYUT GOLD</strong></u>&nbsp;- after paying for 35 nights for the calendar year and filling the questionnaire, you will be provided with UYUT GOLD card, and you will have a right to have the following bonuses and privileges: Guaranteed reservation (if the request is received not later than 48 hours before); Late check-out (18 hours); 7% discount for accommodation in Uyut hotel; 10% discount for Uyut restaurant services and mini-bar in the guestroom; 5% discount for Sauna and Massage services Welcome Gift</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><u>UYUT PLATINUM</u></strong>&nbsp;- after paying for 55 nights for the calendar year and filling the questionnaire, you will be provided with UYUT PLATINUM card and you will have a right to have the following bonuses and privileges: Guaranteed reservation (if the request is received not later than 24 hours before); Late check-out (up to 20 hours); 10% discount for accommodation in Uyut hotel; 15% discount for Uyut restaurant services and mini-bar in the guestroom; 10% discount for Sauna and Massage services; One free-of-charge weekend in Uyut hotel per a year; Welcome Gif&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, N