ssed by Seifullin Street, Almaty,</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">Tel.: +7 (727)&nbsp; 279-51-11, 279-55-11, 279-95-11 моb.+7-777-218-31-32;Fax:&nbsp; +7&nbsp;(727)&nbsp; 279-89-79;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">e-mail:&nbsp; <a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.ru\">hotel_uyut@mail.ru</a>, <a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.kz\">hotel_uyut@mail.kz</a>,</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><a href=\"mailto:reservation@hotel-uyut.kz\">reservation@hotel-uyut.kz</a>, web-сайт: <a href=\"http://www.hotel-uyut.kz/\">www.hotel-uyut.kz</a>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><a name=\"p6\"></a>Book a Luxe Room Package</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b>DEAR LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,</b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n    <li>A fresh newspaper in the room.</li>\r\n    <li>You will be able to enjoy a cup of coffee using the coffee machine at any time.</li>\r\n    <li>If desired, you may have breakfast in the room.</li>\r\n    <li>We will prepare a room for the night stay.</li>\r\n    <li>You can also use the emergency laundry services at the regular price.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b>ALL THESE SERVICES ARE COMPLETELY FREE IF YOU BOOK A</b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b>&nbsp;LUXE ROOM</b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><i><u>OUR ADDRESS</u></i>&nbsp; 127/1 Gogol street crossed by Seifullin Street, Almaty,</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">Tel.: +7 (727)&nbsp; 279-51-11, 279-55-11, 279-95-11 моb.+7-777-218-31-32; Fax:&nbsp; +7&nbsp;(727)&nbsp; 279-89-79;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">e-mail:&nbsp; <a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.ru\">hotel_uyut@mail.ru</a>, <a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.kz\">hotel_uyut@mail.kz</a>,</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><a href=\"mailto:reservation@hotel-uyut.kz\">reservation@hotel-uyut.kz</a>, web-сайт: <a href=\"http://www.hotel-uyut.kz/\">www.hotel-uyut.kz</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><a name=\"p7\"></a>Stay for Three Nights and Pay for Two Nights Only Package</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b>DEAR LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,</b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">We are glad to offer you a &lsquo;Stay for three nights and pay for two</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">nights only&rsquo; package</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">The price includes the services of fitness center, sauna open 8 am to 10 pm, buffet breakfast, WI-FI internet, and 12% VAT.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <u>Terms of booking: </u></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>The offer is valid Fridays through Sundays.&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li>Accommodation for 3 nights minimum, the 3<sup>rd</sup> night is free of charge.</li>\r\n    <li>Cancellation should be made 48 hours prior.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Number of rooms for this offer is limited, and the offer is not extend to the Economy Rooms.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The package&rsquo;s services are valid only on a stay date and are not compensated by the hotel.</div>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><i><u>OUR ADDRESS</u></i>&nbsp; 127/1 Gogol street crossed by Seifullin Street, Almaty,</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">Tel.: +7 (727)&nbsp; 279-51-11, 279-55-11, 279-95-11 моb.+7-777-218-31-32; Fax:&nbsp; +7&nbsp;(727)&nbsp; 279-89-79;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">e-mail:&nbsp; <a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.ru\">hotel_uyut@mail.ru</a>, <a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.kz\">hotel_uyut@mail.kz</a>,</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><a href=\"mailto:reservation@hotel-uyut.kz\">reservation@hotel-uyut.kz</a>, web-сайт: <a href=\"http://www.hotel-uyut.kz/\">www.hotel-uyut.kz</a>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><a name=\"p8\"></a>Happy Birthday Special Offer</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">\r\n<div align=\"center\"><b>DEAR LADIES AND GENTLEMEN</b><b>!</b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />\r\nWe offer you aprogram of &quot;Happy Birthday, dear guest!&quot;.We congratulate you onthis wonderfulholiday andwantto please you. As the saying goes: &quot;My years - mywealth.&quot;Soon this daywill receive a discountonaccommodation, which is equal to the numberof complete years.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">The program isvalidonly on the dayof your birth.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><i><u>OUR ADDRESS</u></i>&nbsp; 127/1 Gogol street crossed by Seifullin Street, Almaty,</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">Tel.: +7 (727)&nbsp; 279-51-11, 279-55-11, 279-95-11 моb.+7-777-218-31-32; Fax:&nbsp; +7&nbsp;(727)&nbsp; 279-89-79;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">e-mail:&nbsp; <a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.ru\">hotel_uyut@mail.ru</a>, <a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.kz\">hotel_uyut@mail.kz</a>,</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><a href=\"mailto:reservation@hotel-uyut.kz\">reservation@hotel-uyut.kz</a>, web-сайт: <a href=\"http://www.hotel-uyut.kz/\">www.hotel-uyut.kz</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><a name=\"p11\"></a>Our Colleague Special Offer</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>&nbsp;</b><b>DEAR COLLEAGUES,</b></div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">We are always happy to see you at our hotel!</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">Therefore, we offer to employees of hotels and travel companies of the Republic of Kazakhstan, the CIS and neighboring countries a discount of 20% for the entire period of stay.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><u>The offer includes:</u></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Accommodation in room;&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li>Buffet breakfast;</li>\r\n    <li>Fitness center;</li>\r\n    <li>Sauna, 8 am to 10 pm;</li>\r\n    <li>Free WI-FI internet;</li>\r\n    <li>12% VAT;</li>\r\n    <li>Free Parking</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">The offer is valid any day of the week.</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">Number of rooms for this offer is not limited.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><u>Terms of booking:</u></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>You should provide us with a letter of confirmation on behalf of management of your hotel or travel company on a letterhead;</li>\r\n    <li>When booking by phone or e-mail, please indicate the name of the package &lsquo;Our colleague&rsquo;.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><i><u>OUR ADDRESS</u></i>&nbsp; 127/1 Gogol street crossed by Seifullin Street, Almaty,</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">Tel.: +7 (727)&nbsp; 279-51-11, 279-55-11, 279-95-11 моb.+7-777-218-31-32;Fax:&nbsp; +7&nbsp;(727)&nbsp; 279-89-79;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">e-mail:&nbsp; <a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.ru\">hotel_uyut@mail.ru</a>, <a href=\"mailto:hotel_uyut@mail.kz\">hotel_uyut@mail.kz</a>,</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><a href=\"mailto:reservation@hotel-uyut.kz\">reservation@hotel-uyut.kz</a>, web-сайт: <a href=\"http://www.hotel-uyut.kz/\">www.hotel-uyut.kz</a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><a name=\"p12\"></a>Offers for families who adopts the children from Kazakhstan Special Offer</h2>\r\n<div><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">The families with children can be provided with the following: extra bed if required; bassinets or playpen; potty; highchair; toys; device for heating of feeding bottles; electric kettle; two kinds of cooked cereals for breakfast, home-made milk and kefir, diabetic diet.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><a name=\"p13\"></a>Permanent Guest Program</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our hotel provides for the Permanent Guest Program. We offer the bonuses and discounts system which corresponds to the number of your guestrooms:</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><u>UYUT SILVER&nbsp;</u></strong>&ndash; after paying for 10 nights for the calendar year and filling the questionnaire you will be provided with UYUT SILVER card, and you will have a right to have the following bonuses and privileges:</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Guaranteed reservation (if the request is received not later than 72 hours before);</li>\r\n    <li>Late check-out (16 hours);</li>\r\n    <li>5% discount for accommodation in Uyut hotel;</li>\r\n    <li>5% discount for Uyut restaurant services and mini-bar in the guestroom;</li>\r\n    <li>Welcome Gift &nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><u><strong>UYUT GOLD</strong></u>&nbsp;- after paying for 35 nights for the calendar year and filling the questionnaire, you will be provided with UYUT GOLD card, and you will have a right to have the following bonuses and privileges:</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Guaranteed reservation (if the request is received not later than 48 hours before);</li>\r\n    <li>Late check-out (16 hours);</li>\r\n    <li>10% discount for accommodation in Uyut hotel;</li>\r\n    <li>10% discount for Uyut restaurant services and mini-bar in the guestroom;</li>\r\n    <li>5% discount for Sauna.</li>\r\n    <li>Welcome Gift</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><u>UYUT PLATINUM</u></strong>&nbsp;- after paying for 55 nights for the calendar year and filling the questionnaire, you will be provided with UYUT PLATINUM card and you will have a right to have the following bonuses and privileges:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Guaranteed reservation (if the request is received not later than 24 hours before);</li>\r\n    <li>Late check-out (up to 16 hours);</li>\r\n    <li>15% discount for accommodation in Uyut hotel;</li>\r\n    <li>15% discount for Uyut restaurant services and mini-bar in the guestroom; 1</li>\r\n    <li>10% discount for Sauna &nbsp;services;</li>\r\n    <li>One free-of-charge weekend in Uyut hotel per a year;</li>\r\n    <li>Welcome Gif&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
