pan><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">7000</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">坚戈，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">5800</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\nSimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">坚戈；半膳宿&mdash;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">3500</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">坚戈，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">2900</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\nSimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">坚戈。折扣灵活。宾馆有警卫看守</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:15.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">会议厅容纳</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">100,30,30</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">人，可以在方便、宜人的环境中组织事务性会见，配有一切必要设备，可保证事务性会见、交际活动的质量，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">Уют</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">饭店的内部装修为意大利风格。这里您可以品尝到亚洲菜肴，东西方菜系。饭店提供所有条件，可进行</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">50-70</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">人的宴会、推介会、大典礼，可组织茶会、商务午餐、冷餐会、餐饮并提供服务。大堂吧</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">24</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">小时营业。夏天小广场上还会有葱郁的树木和欢快作响的喷泉。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:15.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">为了让您全身心放松，拥有好心情，宾馆还提供欧式桑拿，有舒适的芬兰蒸汽室，客厅，休息室，按摩室，温水泳池，按摩师服务，电离子电视，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">KTV</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">DVD</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">，餐厅服务，停车场。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:15.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">宾馆为我们的客人还提供如下服务：昼夜预定，全天候的送餐服务，商务中心，纪念品商店，洗衣和干洗服务，每日免费桑拿，交通服务，外国公民登记，熨衣间，枕头菜单，寄存室，前台的保险柜，国际电话业务，自动柜员机，终端机，停车场。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:15.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" open=\"\" new=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" open=\"\" new=\"\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">宾馆里可用信用卡</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:SimS